<text><body><cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0178a" xml:id="I01.0071.0178a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0178a01"/><cb:docNumber>No. 71</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0178a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>陳神忻七十二人等造石室記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb n="0179a" xml:id="I01.0071.0179a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0179a00"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陽</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陽</head><cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0179a01"/><p xml:id="pI01p0179a0101" cb:type="pre">當陽像主衛買興
<lb ed="I" n="0179a02"/>香火主清信士女衛姿容
<lb ed="I" n="0179a03"/>唯大齊皇建二年歲次<note n="0179001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨐌＝辛【史】</note><note n="0179001" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨐌【佛拓】，辛【史】</note><app n="0179001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辛</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">𨐌</rdg></app>巳五月
<lb ed="I" n="0179a04"/>丙午<note n="0179002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30957"/>＝朔【史】</note><note n="0179002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30957"/>【佛拓】，朔【史】</note><app n="0179002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朔</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30957"/></rdg></app>廿五日庚午。并州樂平郡
<lb ed="I" n="0179a05"/>石艾縣安鹿交村邑義陳神忻。合
<lb ed="I" n="0179a06"/>□邑子七十二人<note n="0179003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䒭＝等【史】</note><note n="0179003" resp="ihp" type="mod">䒭【佛拓】，等【史】</note><app n="0179003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">等</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">䒭</rdg></app>。敬造石室一
<lb ed="I" n="0179a07"/>區。今得成<note n="0179004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB02193"/>＝就【史】</note><note n="0179004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB02193"/>【佛拓】，就【史】</note><app n="0179004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">就</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB02193"/></rdg></app>。上為佛法興隆。又<note n="0179005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30779"/>＝願【史】</note><note n="0179005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30779"/>【佛拓】，願【史】</note><app n="0179005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">願</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30779"/></rdg></app>皇
<lb ed="I" n="0179a08"/>帝陛下。金輪應庭。聖祚凝遠。群遼
<lb ed="I" n="0179a09"/>宰守。貢謁以時。國土安寧。兵駕不
<lb ed="I" n="0179a10"/><note n="0179006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30858"/>＝起【史】</note><note n="0179006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30858"/>【佛拓】，起【史】</note><app n="0179006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">起</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30858"/></rdg></app>。五<note n="0179007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣖫＝穀【史】</note><note n="0179007" resp="ihp" type="mod">𣖫【佛拓】，穀【史】</note><app n="0179007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">穀</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">𣖫</rdg></app>熟成。人民安樂。下為七世
<lb ed="I" n="0179a11"/>先亡。見存師僧父母。因緣眷。蠢動
<lb ed="I" n="0179a12"/><note n="0179008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">罘＝眾【史】</note><note n="0179008" resp="ihp" type="mod">罘【佛拓】，眾【史】</note><app n="0179008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">眾</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">罘</rdg></app>生。有形之<note n="0179009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30976"/>＝類【史】</note><note n="0179009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30976"/>【佛拓】，類【史】</note><app n="0179009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">類</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30976"/></rdg></app>。<note n="0179010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30977"/>＝越【史】</note><note n="0179010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30977"/>【佛拓】，越【史】</note><app n="0179010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">越</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30977"/></rdg></app>三途之<note n="0179011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB25812"/>＝苦【史】</note><note n="0179011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB25812"/>【佛拓】，苦【史】</note><app n="0179011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">苦</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB25812"/></rdg></app><note n="0179012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30978"/>＝難【史】</note><note n="0179012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30978"/>【佛拓】，難【史】</note><app n="0179012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">難</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30978"/></rdg></app>。居
<lb ed="I" n="0179a13"/>登政覺。
<lb ed="I" n="0179a14"/>八<note n="0179013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">閞＝關【史】</note><note n="0179013" resp="ihp" type="mod">閞【佛拓】，關【史】</note><app n="0179013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">關</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">閞</rdg></app>齋主呂<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">和</unclear>　　　　　進
<lb ed="I" n="0179a15"/>齋主扳授恒州
<lb ed="I" n="0179a16"/>齋主藉<note n="0179014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30979"/>＝雙【史】</note><note n="0179014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30979"/>【佛拓】，雙【史】</note><app n="0179014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">雙</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30979"/></rdg></app>憐
<lb ed="I" n="0179a17"/>齋主王保愛
<lb ed="I" n="0179a18"/>齋主施<app type="star" corresp="#0179014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">雙</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30979"/></rdg></app>任
<lb ed="I" n="0179a19"/>齋主暢景略　齋主暢又為父母
<lb ed="I" n="0179a20"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0179a21"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0179a22"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0179a23"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0179a24"/>輪王主張德仁
<lb ed="I" n="0179a25"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">衝</unclear>天王主張黑仁</p></cb:div></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0179b" xml:id="I01.0071.0179b" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0179b00"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之二　碑陰</cb:mulu><head>之二　碑陰</head><cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0179b01"/><p xml:id="pI01p0179b0101" cb:type="pre">邑主陳神忻邑子衛萇洛邑子衛強珍
<lb ed="I" n="0179b02"/>邑子衛天勝邑子樂和仁邑子衛高□
<lb ed="I" n="0179b03"/>邑子王領悅邑子王牛山邑子王阿□
<lb ed="I" n="0179b04"/>邑子楊阿安邑子韓智悅邑子張惡仁
<lb ed="I" n="0179b05"/>邑子衛伯達邑子衛始儁邑子衛阿陽
<lb ed="I" n="0179b06"/>邑子衛北陽邑子王阿標邑子郭張□
<lb ed="I" n="0179b07"/>邑子王曇信邑子衛宗和邑子衛元伯
<lb ed="I" n="0179b08"/>邑子張元伯邑子衛□□邑子王遵勝
<lb ed="I" n="0179b09"/>邑子侯阿顯邑子衛婆仁邑子張進国
<lb ed="I" n="0179b10"/>邑子衛阿義邑子衛阿季邑子陳阿慧
<lb ed="I" n="0179b11"/>邑子衛董定邑子張相如邑子張黑仁
<lb ed="I" n="0179b12"/>邑子衛顯和邑子張法山邑子張万保
<lb ed="I" n="0179b13"/>邑子郭阿統邑子張阿斥邑子郭進伯
<lb ed="I" n="0179b14"/>邑子衛元穆邑子衛阿斛邑子張阿貴
<lb ed="I" n="0179b15"/>邑子衛祖欣邑子衛宣德邑子郭神龜
<lb ed="I" n="0179b16"/>邑子王貴遵邑子王長孫邑子張阿奴
<lb ed="I" n="0179b17"/>邑子張轉勝邑子李迴族邑子王崇先
<lb ed="I" n="0179b18"/>邑子張阿渥邑子楮元勝邑子衛阿<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">侯</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0179b19"/>邑子李<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">貴</unclear>勝邑子李小勝邑子尹姿羅
<lb ed="I" n="0179b20"/>邑子藉顯貴邑子衛舍欣邑子衛令欣
<lb ed="I" n="0179b21"/>邑子衛文貴邑子張<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">永</unclear>賓邑子李思祖
<lb ed="I" n="0179b22"/>邑子張強族邑子張顯和邑子張蘭得
<lb ed="I" n="0179b23"/>上為亡父。見存阿婆。先亡
<lb ed="I" n="0179b24"/>兄。因緣眷屬。一時成佛。
<lb ed="I" n="0179b25"/>當陽像主張強族</p></cb:div></cb:div>
